So it's your choice.

40:10.284 --> 40:20.094
I'm making the choice to push off the dock of the bay and go out into the deep waters so that we can do something great for children and reach more homes and more souls for Christ.

40:21.275 --> 40:27.222
And it's your choice to say, as He follows Christ, I'm with that guy.

40:28.703 --> 40:32.927
And together, we're going to get something great done for our God.

40:33.988 --> 40:35.570
We're going to follow Him.

40:36.386 --> 40:42.597
Brethren, be followers together of me and mark them which follow so as you have us for an ensemble.

40:43.318 --> 40:47.585
May we be a people going after Christ like the Apostle Paul did.

40:48.206 --> 40:57.101
May we be a people following God's simple pattern in a day when Satan tries to so cause us to hear so many voices and go so many ways.

40:57.522 --> 41:00.948
May we be striving together for the faith of the gospel.

